data.description: This is IT, the one you've been looking for! Updated home in Wylie ISD! Walk into a vaulted entry with beautiful chandelier, stairway with breezeway overlooking the semi-open concept living, dining, and kitchen area. This home has so much to offer with 3 separate living areas, three fireplaces, study, 5 bedrooms, and two staircases! Let your imagination go wild with game room possibilities, or potential in-law suite! The Owner's suite is on the first level with privacy and comfort in mind. See through fireplace from bedroom into the luxurious bathroom. The kitchen is a showstopper with a Texas Sized island, GE Monogram appliances, 6 burner gas range, and fantastic cabinetry.  All of the interior gets even better with the large sunroom that opens out into an expansive backyard oasis! Large swimming pool with sunning space, separate jacuzzi, barbeque area, and an RV garage or workshop! All of this, and there is a private lake in the subdivision as well! New roof to be installed as well.
